(850, 'Haut', 'Vendor', 20, 'Vendor', 80, 'Homme', 'Jaune', ' Part of the collaboration series with Maison Kitsuné, this classic cut t-shirt features an original illustration print to the back.\r\n\r\n- 100% cotton\r\n- Ribbed crewneck\r\n- Short sleeves\r\n- Rib-knit trim crewneck\r\n- Fox and triangle patches embroidered at chest\r\n- Printed original illustration to the back\r\n- Relaxed fit\r\n\r\nAND WANDER was launched in 2011 with the idea of combining a profound love of the outdoors with an approach to production and design that was reminiscent of Paris collection fashion brands. Merging the worlds of mountain inspired outdoor wear with high fashion design sensibilities, AND WANDER\'s creations are original, authentic, functional and of the highest quality.\r\n\r\nMaison Kitsuné is a French fashion and music label that was founded in 2002 by Gildas Loaëc and Masaya Kuroki. The multi-faceted brand is known for its unique blend of Parisian and Japanese aesthetics, combining contemporary clothing designs with classic elements of French and Japanese culture.\r\n\r\nVAD-T3802002\r\nPOLYESTER 51% COTTON 49%\r\nMADE IN CHINA', 0, 'img/Vetements/850/'),
